{"tid":737471,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先我喺7 11一嘢發爛渣揼曬啲辣椒油落地下","createTime":"2018-07-11T01:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T04:23:20.000Z","uid":99568,"like":31,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f30f04bc17ec8fd7fbb1ea617cd82102680738","tid":737471,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:26:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老味啱啱邊個間7仔見好耐冇食過魚蛋就入去整番一兜， 但係因為我八達通冇錢所以我要增值先，嗰個死廢老阿姐 已經大大聲聲喺度話你究竟想做邊樣呀， 我都不失霸氣咁回應返佢一句， 增值先 然之後再要一兜魚蛋， 跟住佢用鄙視嘅眼神望一望我， 我又用黃子華嘅眼神啤一啤番佢， 我見佢好唔順氣咁喺度幫我不夾魚蛋， 跟住我禮禮貌貌同佢講話唔該我想要咖哩嗰隻唔係要原味， 跟住我聽到佢 細細聲喺度口噏噏（ 頭先又唔早講） 我聽到呢句已經忍無可忍， 所以我已 九秒9速度即刻食曬啲魚蛋， 然後我 一夜 將嗰兜魚蛋嘅咖哩辣椒油抌曬落地下， 然後頭也不回插袋慢慢行出7仔， 喺呢一刻， 我終於做咗人中之龍！"},{"pid":"c66bf04775ac2a2ce97e7ad7626f20faf49085e7","tid":737471,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9624f1e1ec08bbce1b0f2a7188be25afe23eab","tid":737471,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"7d47703328e6c04dfd4981f6343cac8b58aa6fa9","tid":737471,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3179548e2e70f91a59c57eb41799c27f7d8509","tid":737471,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:27:47.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔係咁易恰的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9344b7a8b39eca0c3a9f1ef4b7736281204a62f9","tid":737471,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-